Chairman Yang Hoon is denying all charges.

00:50:36.283 --> 00:50:38.118
People are paying attention to

00:50:38.201 --> 00:50:40.829
how the Special Investigation Unit
of prosecution

00:50:40.912 --> 00:50:42.622
will prove the charges.

00:50:42.748 --> 00:50:44.291
THE 23RD PRESIDENTIAL TRANSITION TEAM

00:50:44.374 --> 00:50:46.168
Check this side now.

00:50:46.251 --> 00:50:48.754
-It's crooked!
-I'm reeling in now.

00:50:48.837 --> 00:50:51.214
-Pull.
-I'm reeling in.

00:51:03.143 --> 00:51:04.478
President-elect, smile.

00:51:04.561 --> 00:51:06.313
Can you strike an encouraging pose?

00:51:07.022 --> 00:51:09.941
How is it going
with Chairman Yang's investigation?

00:51:11.276 --> 00:51:13.403
The prosecution will do the investigation.

00:51:13.487 --> 00:51:14.446
Come on.

00:51:14.946 --> 00:51:17.532
Chairman Yang and Cha Su-yeon are family.

00:51:18.200 --> 00:51:21.703
Everyone in politics and finance
is related by marriage.

00:51:21.787 --> 00:51:24.080
Chairman Yang and Cha Su-yeon are special.

00:51:24.164 --> 00:51:27.459
Chairman Yang's father
supported him in every way possible,

00:51:27.542 --> 00:51:29.294
and everyone knows that.

00:51:29.377 --> 00:51:33.465
But as soon as the president-elect
brought up the special bill,

00:51:33.548 --> 00:51:34.925
they started investigating

00:51:35.008 --> 00:51:38.053
Chairman Yang,
as if to respond to his action.

00:51:39.137 --> 00:51:40.597
What a coincidence.

00:51:41.389 --> 00:51:43.141
What do you want to say?

00:51:43.225 --> 00:51:45.769
President Yu might be holding Cha hostage

00:51:45.852 --> 00:51:49.231
and sending warning signs
to the president-elect.

00:51:49.314 --> 00:51:51.066
That he can't pass the special bill.

00:51:56.363 --> 00:51:58.240
Why won't you say anything?

00:51:59.825 --> 00:52:01.451
If I say anything, you'll put it

00:52:01.535 --> 00:52:05.038
in your article saying it was
the president-elect's attendant's words.

00:52:05.121 --> 00:52:07.415
You won't fall for it.

00:52:07.499 --> 00:52:10.502
-Please look here.
-Please move forward to take photos.

00:52:12.379 --> 00:52:16.007
By the way,
when will he come to my news magazine?

00:52:16.675 --> 00:52:18.718
As soon as I sort out the schedule.

00:52:18.802 --> 00:52:21.221
If you come to mine last
after going to others

00:52:21.304 --> 00:52:24.099
like you did during the election,
I'll get really upset.

00:52:24.933 --> 00:52:26.476
You sure hold a grudge.

00:52:26.560 --> 00:52:28.687
The schedule got messed up then.

00:52:37.654 --> 00:52:39.114
Let's take pictures.

00:52:40.156 --> 00:52:42.158
One, two, three.

00:52:42.242 --> 00:52:43.994
Did you see our election broadcast?

00:52:44.077 --> 00:52:47.372
I practically wrote a whole epic for him.

00:52:47.455 --> 00:52:49.749
I helped out
with the start of the new regime,

00:52:49.833 --> 00:52:51.126
so come to my show first.

00:52:52.460 --> 00:52:55.255
I got it. Don't worry.

00:52:56.756 --> 00:53:00.594
I'll need to ask you a favor after favor
for the upcoming five years.

00:53:00.677 --> 00:53:02.053
Right.

00:53:02.762 --> 00:53:04.848
What happened yesterday?

00:53:04.931 --> 00:53:06.433
Yesterday?

00:53:06.516 --> 00:53:08.810
When we called the president-elect
from the studio.

00:53:12.689 --> 00:53:14.107
What is it?

00:53:14.190 --> 00:53:16.902
I freaked out thinking
it would be messed up.

00:53:16.985 --> 00:53:20.572
If it weren't for me cleaning up the mess,
things would've been really bad.

00:53:21.781 --> 00:53:24.326
Where on earth was he?

00:53:25.452 --> 00:53:27.829
Let's do a cheer.

00:53:28.538 --> 00:53:29.873
One, two, three.

00:53:29.956 --> 00:53:31.333
-Let's go!
-Let's go!

00:53:33.084 --> 00:53:34.419
Don't tell me

00:53:35.754 --> 00:53:37.339
he disappeared without telling you.

00:53:38.548 --> 00:53:39.758
At that hour?

00:53:53.897 --> 00:53:55.315
Exactly on time.

00:54:04.824 --> 00:54:06.785
Excuse me, what is this?

00:54:08.745 --> 00:54:10.497
What's happening?

00:54:11.498 --> 00:54:13.792
I don't know, it's too sudden.

00:54:13.875 --> 00:54:15.043
Let's check and talk later.

00:54:15.126 --> 00:54:18.213
Who sent these? Tell us.

00:54:18.964 --> 00:54:21.091
Where did these come from?
Haseong-dong, right?

00:54:21.174 --> 00:54:23.426
-Who sent these?
-What's inside?

00:54:23.969 --> 00:54:24.844
-What is it?
-Tell us.

00:54:26.221 --> 00:54:27.639
You can say where it came from.

00:54:27.722 --> 00:54:29.516
-What's inside?
-Sorry.

00:54:30.183 --> 00:54:31.309
Tell us.

00:54:31.393 --> 00:54:33.103
Who sent these, then?

00:54:33.186 --> 00:54:35.021
-Tell us.
-What?

00:54:50.370 --> 00:54:51.913
Cha Su-yeon sent them indeed.

00:54:56.751 --> 00:54:57.836
We'll head to the hospital.

00:54:58.420 --> 00:54:59.838
Did you see the photo I sent?

00:55:00.880 --> 00:55:03.216
His stuff was delivered to the office.

00:55:03.299 --> 00:55:05.927
I checked, and it was sent by Cha Su-yeon.

00:55:06.970 --> 00:55:10.015
It's divorce. Use that exact word.

00:55:10.098 --> 00:55:13.101
Dig up evidence that Cha is involved
in Yang's succession

00:55:13.184 --> 00:55:15.103
and fallouts between her and her husband--

00:55:16.104 --> 00:55:17.313
Checking the facts?

00:55:17.814 --> 00:55:20.150
What I'm seeing at the scene is the fact.

00:55:20.233 --> 00:55:22.736
His wife kicked him out
on the very first day,

00:55:22.819 --> 00:55:24.612
and you want to check the facts?

00:55:24.696 --> 00:55:26.031
Say something.

00:55:30.535 --> 00:55:32.412
It's not just divorce.

00:55:32.996 --> 00:55:34.205
It's a divorce war.

00:55:35.165 --> 00:55:38.001
Nothing has been confirmed yet.

00:55:38.084 --> 00:55:39.836
We'll end it here. Thank you.

00:55:41.171 --> 00:55:42.005
Watch out!

00:55:56.853 --> 00:56:00.315
The president-elect and his wife's
divorce rumor caused a huge stir.

00:56:02.734 --> 00:56:04.486
Some are speculating that

00:56:04.569 --> 00:56:08.531
the divorce is caused by Chairman Yang's
illegal succession investigation.

00:56:08.615 --> 00:56:13.203
The accusations made by the politicians
about Cha being the mastermind

00:56:13.286 --> 00:56:15.413
behind the scenes has surfaced again.

00:56:15.497 --> 00:56:17.749
With the claim that
the reason behind the divorce

00:56:17.832 --> 00:56:20.543
is that the prosecution
discovered the evidence of

00:56:20.627 --> 00:56:23.546
Cha being involved
in Chairman Yang's succession…

00:56:28.218 --> 00:56:29.385
What is it?

00:56:29.928 --> 00:56:31.387
What happened?

00:56:31.471 --> 00:56:32.430
I don't know.

00:56:33.306 --> 00:56:35.391
I said I'd go back as soon as I ate.

00:56:35.475 --> 00:56:36.643
Go back to the wake.

00:56:36.726 --> 00:56:38.436
There's no need to.

00:56:38.520 --> 00:56:40.271
Nobody stops by anyway.

00:56:40.355 --> 00:56:43.566
That's why someone should be there.

00:56:43.650 --> 00:56:45.318
We can't make him feel lonely.

00:56:45.401 --> 00:56:47.195
It was the president's special order.

00:56:47.278 --> 00:56:49.614
Why are you so rude to your older brother?

00:56:49.697 --> 00:56:51.324
Seriously.

00:56:51.407 --> 00:56:54.285
Don't call yourself older anything.
You were born five minutes early.

00:56:54.911 --> 00:56:56.037
Let's go.

00:56:56.121 --> 00:56:56.955
Wait.

00:56:57.038 --> 00:56:59.874
Can I eat one cup noodles
at a convenience store?

00:57:00.500 --> 00:57:03.920
I've been having yukgaejang all day long,
and I'm sick of it.

00:57:04.003 --> 00:57:06.047
You gobbled up
all the boiled pork yourself.

00:57:06.131 --> 00:57:07.924
I'm glad you got sick of it.

00:57:08.007 --> 00:57:11.553
You had a grand feast
as if you were filming an eating show.

00:57:11.636 --> 00:57:14.264
A mourner needs to be on a full stomach.

00:57:16.307 --> 00:57:18.351
You should stop running the channel

00:57:18.435 --> 00:57:20.937
about Cha Su-yeon
and start an eating show.

00:57:21.020 --> 00:57:23.314
You're a big eater.

00:57:23.398 --> 00:57:24.899
You were born to be.

00:57:24.983 --> 00:57:27.819
-Eating suits you, not fashion.
-Be quiet!

00:57:31.197 --> 00:57:32.615
Here.

00:57:32.699 --> 00:57:35.034
Come back a few more times
to get it redressed.

00:57:35.118 --> 00:57:36.744
Make sure it's not infected.

00:57:39.247 --> 00:57:40.457
Nurse?

00:57:40.540 --> 00:57:42.333
I think you should come out.

00:57:42.417 --> 00:57:45.336
The reporters are forcing their way in.

00:57:45.420 --> 00:57:46.504
What?

00:57:47.589 --> 00:57:49.507
-Hello?
-Madam!

00:57:58.850 --> 00:58:00.435
It's Cha Su-yeon.

00:58:02.270 --> 00:58:04.230
Why run away? We did nothing wrong.

00:58:04.314 --> 00:58:06.441
-There she is!
-Miss Cha Su-yeon!

00:58:07.734 --> 00:58:09.235
Divorce is a private matter.

00:58:09.319 --> 00:58:11.112
I can't let them take your photo.

00:58:11.196 --> 00:58:12.780
Why? Everyone already knows my face.

00:58:14.324 --> 00:58:15.325
It's different.

00:58:15.408 --> 00:58:16.701
What's different?

00:58:17.911 --> 00:58:19.162
The elevator.

00:58:19.913 --> 00:58:20.955
Don't think so.

00:58:21.039 --> 00:58:22.999
Mom!

00:58:23.082 --> 00:58:24.501
The photos they take now

00:58:24.584 --> 00:58:26.794
will mark you and haunt you forever.

00:58:26.878 --> 00:58:28.671
Please just listen to me.

00:58:30.215 --> 00:58:32.050
Where is she? Miss Cha Su-yeon!

00:58:32.133 --> 00:58:33.593
The stairs!

00:58:33.676 --> 00:58:36.804
-Miss Cha!
-Miss Cha, tell us your thoughts.

00:58:41.351 --> 00:58:42.352
Madam, where are you now?

00:58:42.936 --> 00:58:43.811
Meet me in front.

00:58:43.895 --> 00:58:45.772
Not the front, come to the back door.

00:58:45.855 --> 00:58:47.607
I parked my car there.

00:58:49.359 --> 00:58:51.319
-Miss Cha, say something!
-Stop there, Miss Cha!

00:58:51.861 --> 00:58:53.112
You can refute the rumors now,

00:58:53.196 --> 00:58:54.447
or we'll upload the news as is!

00:58:54.531 --> 00:58:56.824
-Miss Cha, say something!
-Miss Cha!

00:59:02.956 --> 00:59:05.124
Oh? Cha Su-yeon…

00:59:05.208 --> 00:59:06.251
Madam, this way!

00:59:06.334 --> 00:59:08.211
Miss Cha, let's have an interview!

00:59:08.294 --> 00:59:11.506
-Excuse me.
-Is it true that you're getting divorced?

00:59:11.589 --> 00:59:12.840
Hold on, Miss Cha.

00:59:12.924 --> 00:59:14.259
-Miss Cha!
-Miss Cha!

00:59:18.304 --> 00:59:20.390
Let's go to the back door!

00:59:24.352 --> 00:59:25.436
Wear your seat belt.

00:59:29.065 --> 00:59:31.192
Miss Cha Su-yeon! Miss Cha Su-yeon!

00:59:33.570 --> 00:59:34.404
Miss Cha Su-yeon!

00:59:44.038 --> 00:59:44.914
Hurry up!

01:00:11.232 --> 01:00:13.359
-Did you put on your seat belt?
-Yes.

01:00:36.007 --> 01:00:37.175
Mom.

01:00:37.258 --> 01:00:38.509
Hold tight.

01:00:48.936 --> 01:00:50.188
Mom.

01:00:50.271 --> 01:00:51.522
It's okay.

01:00:54.442 --> 01:00:55.943
Did you see that? Poor Ji-yu.

01:00:56.027 --> 01:00:57.737
Were they faking it until now?

01:00:57.820 --> 01:00:58.863
All of that was for show?

01:00:58.946 --> 01:01:01.032
Serves her right.

01:01:01.115 --> 01:01:02.241
Hit rock bottom at once.

01:01:07.997 --> 01:01:09.999
Don't look, Ji-yu. Don't look.

01:01:10.708 --> 01:01:11.751
Mom!

01:02:09.308 --> 01:02:10.810
Let's not result to a lawsuit.

01:02:10.893 --> 01:02:13.187
Let's divorce by consent.

01:02:13.271 --> 01:02:15.398
If you did bug him
as the president-elect claimed,

01:02:15.481 --> 01:02:18.192
isn't it you who broke apart the family?

01:02:18.276 --> 01:02:20.778
I'm divorcing for Su-yeon's sake.

01:02:20.862 --> 01:02:22.196
Don't hurt her anymore.

01:02:22.280 --> 01:02:24.991
You can't get a divorce.

01:02:25.074 --> 01:02:27.660
If you do, you lose your rights
as the first lady.

01:02:27.744 --> 01:02:31.080
I'm the one who made him a president.

01:02:31.164 --> 01:02:35.042
Then I should take half of
what the president owns.

01:02:35.126 --> 01:02:36.210
Isn't that right?

